a-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">About the Institute<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e51cd42 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"e51cd42\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>State Institute of Engineering &amp; Technology (SIET), Panchkula, is a premier government engineering college committed to excellence in technical education and innovation. Established to nurture the next generation of engineers, SIET currently operates from the shared campus of GPP (Government Polytechnic, Panchkula) Sector-26. The institute offers cutting-edge undergraduate programs in Computer Science and Engineering (AI &amp; ML), Computer Science and Engineering (Cyber Security), and Robotics &amp; Automation. With a focus on industry-oriented learning, state-of-the-art facilities, and expert faculty, SIET aims to empower students with the knowledge and skills required to excel in the ever-evolving world of technology. <a href=\"https:\/\/sietpanchkula.ac.in\/the-institute\/\"><strong>read more<\/strong><\/a><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5f368c0 e-flex e-con-boxed elementor-invisible e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"5f368c0\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;,&quot;animation&quot;:&quot;fadeInUp&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0de4a6b elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"0de4a6b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Courses Offered<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-cf6db4b e-grid e-con-full e-con e-child\" data-id=\"cf6db4b\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7e96881 elementor-position-top elementor-position-top elementor-widget elementor-widget-image-box\" data-id=\"7e96881\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image-box.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-image-box-wrapper\"><figure class=\"elementor-image-box-img\"><a href=\"https:\/\/sietpanchkula.ac.in\/computer-science-and-engineering-ai-ml\/\" tabindex=\"-1\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" src=\"https:\/\/sietpanchkula.ac.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/AI-ML.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-image-159\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sietpanchkula.ac.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/AI-ML.jpg 600w, https:\/\/sietpanchkula.ac.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/AI-ML-300x200.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" \/><\/a><\/figure><div class=\"elementor-image-box-content\"><h3 class=\"elementor-image-box-title\"><a href=\"https:\/\/sietpanchkula.ac.in\/computer-science-and-engineering-ai-ml\/\">Computer Science and Engineering (AI &amp; ML)<\/a><\/h3><p class=\"elementor-image-box-description\">Focuses on artificial intelligence and machine learning, covering data science, neural networks, and automation to develop intelligent systems for real-world problem-solving.\n<br \/>\n<b>Intake: 60<\/b><\/p><\/div><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ce9015c elementor-position-top elementor-position-top elementor-widget elementor-widget-image-box\" data-id=\"ce9015c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image-box.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-image-box-wrapper\"><figure class=\"elementor-image-box-img\"><a href=\"https:\/\/sietpanchkula.ac.in\/computer-science-and-engineering-cyber-security\/\" tabindex=\"-1\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" src=\"https:\/\/sietpanchkula.ac.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/Cyber-Security.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-image-161\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sietpanchkula.ac.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/Cyber-Security.jpg 600w, https:\/\/sietpanchkula.ac.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/Cyber-Security-300x200.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" \/><\/a><\/figure><div class=\"elementor-image-box-content\"><h3 class=\"elementor-image-box-title\"><a href=\"https:\/\/sietpanchkula.ac.in\/computer-science-and-engineering-cyber-security\/\">Computer Science and Engineering (Cyber Security)<\/a><\/h3><p class=\"elementor-image-box-description\">Specializes in cybersecurity techniques, ethical hacking, cryptography, and digital forensics to protect systems and networks from cyber threats and ensure data security.\n<br \/>\n<b>Intake: 60<\/b><\/p><\/div><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-14453b2 elementor-position-top elementor-position-top elementor-widget elementor-widget-image-box\" data-id=\"14453b2\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image-box.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-image-box-wrapper\"><figure class=\"elementor-image-box-img\"><a href=\"https:\/\/sietpanchkula.ac.in\/robotics-automation\/\" tabindex=\"-1\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" src=\"https:\/\/sietpanchkula.ac.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/Robotics-Automation.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-image-160\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sietpanchkula.ac.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/Robotics-Automation.jpg 600w, https:\/\/sietpanchkula.ac.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/Robotics-Automation-300x200.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" \/><\/a><\/figure><div class=\"elementor-image-box-content\"><h3 class=\"elementor-image-box-title\"><a href=\"https:\/\/sietpanchkula.ac.in\/robotics-automation\/\">Robotics &amp; Automation<\/a><\/h3><p class=\"elementor-image-box-description\">Integrates mechanical engineering, electronics, and AI to design and develop intelligent robots, automated systems, and smart technologies for industrial and real-world applications.\n<br \/>\n<b>Intake: 60<\/b><\/p><\/div><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-fa027ed e-grid e-con-boxed elementor-invisible e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"fa027ed\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;animation&quot;:&quot;fadeInUp&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c3ade89 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"c3ade89\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4d41937 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"4d41937\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Features<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7e5f21e elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"7e5f21e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default